## SLIDE 4: SYSTEM ARCHITECTURE
Architecture Flow:

Frontend (React.js)
• User Interface
• Form Validation
• State Management
• Navigation
        ↓
Backend (Node.js)
• RESTful APIs
• JWT Auth
• Business Logic
• Data Processing
        ↓
Database (MySQL)
• User Data
• Medical Records
• Appointments
• Profiles

Data Flow:
1. User Request → Frontend UI
2. API Call → Backend Server
3. Authentication → JWT Token Validation
4. Database Query → MySQL Operations
5. Response → Frontend Update

